## 19. 并发执行设计

```java
public class ConcurrentSuiteRunner {

    private final ExecutorService executor =
        Executors.newVirtualThreadPerTaskExecutor();

    public List<SuiteResult> runAll(List<TestSuite> suites, String env) {
        List<CompletableFuture<SuiteResult>> futures = suites.stream()
            .map(suite -> CompletableFuture.supplyAsync(
                () -> runSuite(suite, env), executor))
            .collect(Collectors.toList());

        return futures.stream()
            .map(f -> {
                try {
                    return f.get(10, TimeUnit.MINUTES);
                } catch (TimeoutException e) {
                    return SuiteResult.timeout();
                } catch (InterruptedException | ExecutionException e) {
                    return SuiteResult.error(e);
                }
            })
            .collect(Collectors.toList());
    }

    private SuiteResult runSuite(TestSuite suite, String env) {
        ExecutionContext context = ExecutionContextFactory.create(suite, env);
        return SuiteExecutor.execute(suite, context);
    }
}
```

| 资源 | 隔离方式 |
|------|----------|
| 变量池 | 每个 Suite 独立 ExecutionContext |
| Auth Token | 每个 Suite 独立 AuthProvider 实例 |
| HTTP 连接池 | 每个 Suite 独立 HTTP Client 实例 |
| 报告数据 | 按 executionId 隔离存储 |

